Do you like it?

262
00:29:27.000 --> 00:29:29.195
Great. I think he's dying to get out.

263
00:29:29.600 --> 00:29:32.797
Thank you. very much.
Come back and see us.

264
00:29:37.400 --> 00:29:38.594
Excuse me.

265
00:29:39.560 --> 00:29:41.755
Okay. boys.

266
00:29:54.960 --> 00:29:57.155
