I used to live in hotels
before I lived here.

280
00:31:18.800 --> 00:31:20.074
I do like to cook.

281
00:31:20.640 --> 00:31:22.835
- You like to cook.
- Love to cook.

282
00:31:28.120 --> 00:31:29.758
I bought this for you.

283
00:31:40.400 --> 00:31:42.038
Why don't you just hand it to me?

284
00:31:42.400 --> 00:31:43.833
I like to watch you move.

285
00:31:52.240 --> 00:31:53.275
Okay.

286
