You know that?

292
00:32:51.920 --> 00:32:53.194
Let me hear it.

293
00:32:56.320 --> 00:32:57.355
I hear it.

294
00:32:57.920 --> 00:32:59.797
Can I ask you a question?

295
00:33:01.400 --> 00:33:02.594
Okay.

296
00:33:09.880 --> 00:33:11.552
It is beautiful.

297
00:33:24.720 --> 00:33:25.755
What?

298
00:33:30.560 --> 00:33:31.788
Elizabeth...

299
00:33:32.800 --> 00:33:33.949
...each day at 12:00...

300
00:33:34.880 --> 00:33:37.952
...would you look at that watch
and think of me touching you?

301
00:33:46.120 --> 00:33:47.155
Yes.

302
00:33:50.280 --> 00:33:51.998
Would you do that for me?

303
00:33:54.400 --> 00:33:55.355
Yes.

304
