306
00:34:08.800 --> 00:34:09.755
Who?

307
00:34:10.520 --> 00:34:12.192
I don't believe she said that.

308
00:34:12.800 --> 00:34:14.074
God. what does he want?

309
00:34:15.360 --> 00:34:16.554
I don't know.

310
00:34:17.200 --> 00:34:19.316
I think it's about Farnsworth.

311
