- Here.
- No kidding.

312
00:34:21.800 --> 00:34:22.994
Hello?

313
00:34:23.600 --> 00:34:24.555
Sure. I'll hold.

314
00:34:25.800 --> 00:34:26.915
Such a jerk.

315
00:34:29.320 --> 00:34:30.719
I think I've been hypnotized.

316
