- There's a man on the premises.
- Terrific.

334
00:37:55.600 --> 00:37:56.953
Great. Go to it.

335
00:38:08.960 --> 00:38:10.075
Are these yours?

336
00:38:11.200 --> 00:38:12.394
Yes.

337
00:38:14.480 --> 00:38:16.072
It's nice. Come here.

338
00:38:19.080 --> 00:38:20.513
I don't believe this.

339
