...and I want you
to slide on the floor.

345
00:39:26.520 --> 00:39:27.953
Just lie down on the floor.

346
00:39:28.920 --> 00:39:29.955
Come on.

347
00:39:31.480 --> 00:39:32.595
Go ahead.

348
00:39:37.560 --> 00:39:38.788
Close your eyes.

349
