I didn't.

351
00:40:05.360 --> 00:40:07.555
Promise to keep your eyes closed?

352
00:40:51.480 --> 00:40:52.799
A big one.

353
00:42:15.400 --> 00:42:17.595
Promise to keep your eyes closed.
please.

354
00:42:19.360 --> 00:42:20.475
Stick out your tongue.

355
00:42:22.440 --> 00:42:24.032
Further. Further.

356
00:42:27.040 --> 00:42:28.393
Further. Right.

357
00:42:28.720 --> 00:42:29.311
Yeah.

358
00:42:29.920 --> 00:42:31.797
I'll put it right on the spot.

359
00:42:32.120 --> 00:42:33.155
Yeah.

360
00:42:33.520 --> 00:42:35.192
Oh. that's nice.

361
00:43:18.720 --> 00:43:20.153
I should have said no.

362
00:43:20.760 --> 00:43:21.988
No. no. no.

363
00:43:22.520 --> 00:43:23.953
I should have said no.

364
00:43:24.520 --> 00:43:25.953
I would have if I could have...

365
00:43:26.560 --> 00:43:29.028
...but I couldn't. So I didn't.

366
00:43:34.520 --> 00:43:35.794
Are you talking to me?

367
00:43:39.920 --> 00:43:40.955
Listen. Lizzy...

368
00:43:41.360 --> 00:43:43.396
...you remember when you...

369
00:43:43.800 --> 00:43:46.394
...suggested that I keep your date
with your ex?

370
00:43:47.960 --> 00:43:48.995
Well...

371
00:43:49.400 --> 00:43:50.594
...I did.

372
00:43:52.080 --> 00:43:53.957
And the thing is. I couldn't say no.

373
00:43:57.400 --> 00:43:58.594
I...

374
