...slept with him.

375
00:44:02.680 --> 00:44:04.955
With Bruce? My Bruce?

376
00:44:09.560 --> 00:44:11.039
I thought you should know.

377
00:44:17.600 --> 00:44:19.795
Well. your mom will like him.

378
00:44:20.200 --> 00:44:20.871
Mine did.

379
00:44:24.800 --> 00:44:25.755
Okay.

380
00:44:45.320 --> 00:44:47.788
I'm going to a party tomorrow night
with Molly.

381
00:44:48.880 --> 00:44:49.995
Will you come?

382
